==English==

===Prefix===
'''über-'''

# See [[uber]]

----

==German==

===Preposition===
'''über'''

# [[above]], [[over]]
# [[by]], [[via]]; [[through]]

====Usage notes====
The preposition "&uuml;ber" is used with accusative case if the verb shows movement from one place to another, whereas it is used with dative case if the verb shows location.

